@node KEYBOARD "Arkanos V3.0 - Keyboard commands"

  There are some keys you may need:

    M ......... music on/off
    S ......... sound effects on/off
    F ......... block flashing on/off
    Z ......... ball speed +1, score -40
    P ......... pause game (click mouse button to resume)
    <SPACE> ... shake the level (change ball direction)
    <DEL> ..... restart level and loose only current paddle, no balls
    <ESC> ..... quit current game (did you save the game before ???)
    <F1> ...... show frame rate in top right corner of level
    <F2> ...... change music playing between CIA-timing and VBL-timing
    <F3> ...... display ball moving paths on/off
    <F4> ...... saves debug information; hold <SHIFT> key to save a
                picture of the current level mask
